OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,FA new government rule that will see
OL,7,Fsome high-value farms pay inheritance
OL,8,Ftax came into force yesterday, on
OL,9,FMonday 6 April.
OL,11,FMany farmers say that without other
OL,12,Fstreams of revenue, the changes will
OL,13,Fput them out of business. The
OL,14,FGovernment, and some in the industry,
OL,15,Fsay it makes the system a lot fairer.
OL,17,FBen Chick, who farms in Dorset, said:
OL,18,F"My grandparents have had this
OL,19,Funderstanding for their whole lives
OL,20,Fthat this is what's going to happen.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,F"The inheritance tax has come in
OL,7,Fsuddenly. It's put a lot of financial
OL,8,Fburden on top of their shoulders, the
OL,9,Fmental burden as well, and as the
OL,10,Fyounger ones we're the generation
OL,11,Fthat's got to pay for it. So it's a
OL,12,Freally tricky situation.
OL,14,F"I think the other thing is the timing
OL,15,Fis really bad for farming. Our big
OL,16,Fcash buffer and our way of staying
OL,17,Fprofitable has changed massively."
OL,19,FTo soften the blow of the tax change,
OL,20,Fmany farmers are looking for other
OL,21,Fways to make their money.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,FBen said: "A lot of it is pulling in
OL,7,Fdifferent income streams. So having a
OL,8,Fdiversified business is having
OL,9,Fresilient business that's able to
OL,10,Fweather all the storms of farming and
OL,11,Fworld changes.
OL,13,F"Without that buffer we'd have, in
OL,14,Fterms of different income streams,
OL,15,Fthere'd be no way we could pay
OL,16,Finheritance tax. And I think a
OL,17,Fbusiness that hasn't diversified is
OL,18,Fgoing to be more at risk than one that
OL,19,Fhas."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,FBut Devon farmer Guy Singh-Watson -
OL,7,Fwho set up Riverford, which supplies
OL,8,Forganic vegetable boxes across the UK
OL,9,F- thinks famers should contribute
OL,10,Fmore, despite 'generally being more
OL,11,Fpoorly paid'.
OL,13,FHe said: "When I hear farmers moaning
OL,14,Fabout this (inheritance tax), we have
OL,15,Fto be realistic.
OL,17,F"Yes, life is hard as a farmer needs
OL,18,Fto make an income, but we have a
OL,19,Fwonderful life, we have the benefit
OL,20,Ffrom rising land prices - there's
OL,21,Foptions to sell fields.
OL,26,@vD@LpmvD@\pn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,F"I do urge farmers who complain to
OL,7,Fthink about those people with no
OL,8,Fassets, with no choices, living in a
OL,9,Fone bed flat, on a minimum wage job."
OL,11,FThe policy was initially proposed for
OL,12,Fall farms with a value of #2.5million
OL,13,For more. However, following outrage
OL,14,Fand opposition from farmers, this
OL,15,Ffigure was later increased to
OL,16,F#5million.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said: "I
OL,7,Fthink that is the right balance. I do
OL,8,Fbelieve that if you've got
OL,9,Fagricultural land, if you've got land
OL,10,Fthat's worth more than #5million you
OL,11,Fshould pay through inheritance tax
OL,12,Flike everyone else does.
OL,14,F"But recognising the importance of
OL,15,Ffarming, the limit is that much higher
OL,16,F- #5million for a couple owning a farm
OL,17,Fand the money can be paid back over a
OL,18,F10-year period."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,FSome in the farming community are
OL,7,Fhoping for a silver lining, in farms
OL,8,Fbeing handed down to next generation
OL,9,Fsooner.
OL,11,FChair of NFU Somerset Mark Humphrey
OL,12,Fsaid: "What we'll see now is that some
OL,13,Fof that land will actually move down
OL,14,Fthrough the generations earlier to try
OL,15,Fto save it from being caught in a tax
OL,16,Ftrap at a later generation.
OL,18,F"So it could mean that the younger
OL,19,Fgenerations actually get more involved
OL,20,Fin the business side of their
OL,21,Fbusinesses at an earlier age."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775754356
OL,3,CFarmers in 'tricky situation' as
OL,4,Cinheritance law takes effect
OL,6,FWith livelihoods and legacies at
OL,7,Fstake, the debate on the issue is far
OL,8,Ffrom over.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
